OL,6,FA father who helped lead the fight for
OL,7,Ftruth and justice after his son was
OL,8,Fkilled in the Hillsborough tragedy has
OL,9,Fdied.
OL,11,FPhil Hammond, the former chairman of
OL,12,Fthe Hillsborough Family Support Group
OL,13,F(HFSG), was remembered as a "very
OL,14,Fkind, fair, honest and humble man" by
OL,15,Fother people bereaved in the 1989
OL,16,Fdisaster.
