OL,3,CHillsborough campaigner who lost his
OL,4,Cson in the tragedy has died
OL,6,FHe became a driving force in the
OL,7,Fcampaign after his 14-year-old son
OL,8,FPhilip died in the crush at the
OL,9,FHillsborough stadium in Sheffield
OL,10,Fresulted in the deaths of 97 Liverpool
OL,11,Ffans during the club's FA Cup semi-
OL,12,Ffinal against Nottingham Forest.
OL,14,FHillsborough Survivors Support
OL,15,FAlliance said on X: "We are saddened
OL,16,Fto hear of the passing of Phil
OL,17,FHammond, who was once the chairman of
OL,18,Fthe Hillsborough Family Support Group.
OL,19,FReunited with his son Philip. Our
OL,20,Fthoughts are with his family and
OL,21,Feveryone who knew him ."
