OL,3,CHillsborough campaigner who lost his
OL,4,Cson in the tragedy has died
OL,6,FLiverpool FC added: "All at LFC are
OL,7,Fdeeply saddened to hear of the passing
OL,8,Fof Phil Hammond.
OL,10,F"He lost his 14-year-old son Philip at
OL,11,FHillsborough, went on to become chair
OL,12,Fof the Hillsborough Family Support
OL,13,FGroup and helped lead the fight for
OL,14,Fjustice for the 97. RIP Phil. YNWA"
OL,16,FIn a tribute on X, Louise Brookes,
OL,17,Fwhose brother Andrew died in the
OL,18,Ftragedy, said she was "extremely
OL,19,Fsaddened" to hear of Mr Hammond's
OL,20,Fdeath and described him as "a very
OL,21,Fkind, fair, honest & humble man".
