OL,3,CHillsborough campaigner who lost his
OL,4,Cson in the tragedy has died
OL,6,FA Liverpool City Council spokesman
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is sad news indeed. Phil
OL,8,Fwas a lovely man.
OL,10,F"His role in the fight for truth and
OL,11,Fjustice over the Hillsborough disaster
OL,12,Fwill never be forgotten. May he rest
OL,13,Fin peace."
OL,15,FMr Hammond worked with support group
OL,16,Fsolicitor Ann Adlington to gather
OL,17,Fdocumentary evidence that was sent to
OL,18,Fthe Home Office and led to then-home
OL,19,Fsecretary Jack Straw ordering a new
OL,20,Fprobe.
