OL,3,CHillsborough campaigner who lost his
OL,4,Cson in the tragedy has died
OL,6,FHe grew up in Liverpool's Dingle
OL,7,Fneighbourhood and, after losing his
OL,8,Fright leg in a work accident, become
OL,9,Fmanager of the Lark Lane postal
OL,10,Fsorting office.
OL,12,FThe bereaved families spent years
OL,13,Fcampaigning over a range of issues
OL,14,Fincluding the failure of authorities
OL,15,Fto protect people, attempts to blame
OL,16,Fthe fans and doubts over the original
OL,17,Fcoroner's inquest.
