OL,3,CHillsborough campaigner who lost his
OL,4,Cson in the tragedy has died
OL,6,FIn an interview with The Guardian in
OL,7,F2015, Mr Hammond and his wife Hilda, a
OL,8,Fnurse, remembered Philip as "a joy,
OL,9,Falways".
OL,11,FTheir lives were "complete" as a
OL,12,Ffamily with their second son Graeme,
OL,13,Fwho was 12 when his brother died at
OL,14,FHillsborough, the couple said.
OL,16,FHe also told the newspaper that former
OL,17,Fprime minister David Cameron's
OL,18,Fstatement about Hillsborough in 2012
OL,19,Fwas "the first apology we have had
OL,20,Ffrom anyone in the government for 23
OL,21,Fyears".
