OL,3,CHillsborough campaigner who lost his
OL,4,Cson in the tragedy has died
OL,6,FMr Hammond was secretary, vice-
OL,7,Fchairman and then chairman of the HFSG
OL,8,Ffrom 1999 until 2008, when he suffered
OL,9,Fa brain haemorrhage after banging his
OL,10,Fhead on a shelf while working in the
OL,11,Fgroup's offices.
OL,13,FIn 2014, Mr Hammond was in a
OL,14,Fwheelchair at an inquest into the
OL,15,Fdeaths, listening to the evidence
OL,16,Fincluding from his wife, who
OL,17,Fremembered Philip as a "typical" 14-
OL,18,Fyear-old boy.
