OL,3,CHillsborough campaigner who lost his
OL,4,Cson in the tragedy has died
OL,6,FMrs Hammond told the court their son
OL,7,Fplayed football, was a member of the
OL,8,FBoys' Brigade, loved golf and had the
OL,9,Fodd teen temper tantrum when he would
OL,10,F"stomp up to his bedroom shouting 'I
OL,11,Fhate this house!'".
OL,13,FHis old school, Calderstones in
OL,14,FLiverpool, named its new sports hall
OL,15,Fin his honour, with his parent proudly
OL,16,Fattending the opening ceremony, the
OL,17,Finquest heard.
